docs.lead_paragraph: LEAD: MADDY COHEN had her two children, Matthew and Benjamin, at an age when some parents are worried about paying their children's college tuition. She was just shy of 40 years old when Matthew was born two and a half years ago. She had Benjamin four months ago.
